snippet.title: Bloody Trapland - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Help us get to Steam, vote on Greenlight:
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=92917767

Bloody Trapland is a 2D platformer that takes the trial and error genre to a whole new level!

It's very easy to learn, yet insanely hard to master.

We will be releasing an demo of the game very soon, join us at http://www.facebook.com/BloodyTrapland for your chance to play!

Official site:
http://www.bloodytrapland.com
